[size=4][b]What[/b][/size]

[size=3]Independent scale for nearly every UI surface, plus an extended zoom range so the world isn't fixed at the vanilla 2× – 4×.[/size]

[size=3][b]UI scaling[/b][/size]
[list]
[*][size=3][b]Per-surface scale[/b] — main HUD, action bar, quest tracker, backpack, chat, tooltips, shop, dialogue portraits — each adjustable on its own slider.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Portrait control[/b] — adjust both the position and the scale of character portraits in dialogue, separately from the rest of the dialogue UI.[/size]
[/list]

[size=3][b]Zoom[/b][/size]
[list]
[*][size=3][b]Extended range[/b] — zoom from 0.5× to 10×, compared to the vanilla 2× – 4× cap. Useful for both pixel-peeping and bird's-eye farm planning.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Keybinds[/b] — zoom is bindable to keys, so you don't have to drag the slider mid-play.[/size]
[/list]

[size=3][b]Audio[/b][/size]
[list]
[*][size=3][b]Mute notification sounds[/b] — toggle to silence the small notification chimes if they're cutting through your music.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Other mods of mine you might like[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/37]Easy Living[/url] — adds a taller quest tracker, hides menu noise, plus a stack of other QoL tweaks.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/199]Auto Tools[/url] — automatic tool swapping; pairs well with a properly-sized action bar.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/224]More Jewelry[/url] — six extra jewelry slots in the inventory, with a UI panel that respects your scale settings.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/31]Keep Alive[/url] — required by this mod; keeps everything loaded between play sessions.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Configuration[/b][/size]

[size=3]If you installed the required [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/30]Sun Haven BepInEx Pack[/url] and this mod is configurable, press F1 in-game to open the config interface.[/size]

[size=4][b]Requirements[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/30][size=3]Sun Haven BepInEx Pack[/size][/url]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/31][size=3]Keep Alive[/size][/url]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Compatibility[/b][/size]

[size=3]Built and tested against the latest Steam build of Sun Haven.[/size]

[size=4][b]Installation[/b][/size]

[size=3]Installation using Vortex is the recommended installation method. If you wish to install manually, extract the contents of the mod archive into:

[code]...\steamapps\common\Sun Haven\BepInEx\plugins[/code][/size]

